{"type": "article", "id": 40668, "title": "阿迪达斯把高尔夫卖了，以及，这个意大利泳装新品牌值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-05-11T03:00:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3716, "name": "戴森"}, {"id": 8084, "name": "Marni"}, {"id": 8516, "name": "高尔夫"}, {"id": 9968, "name": "手机壳"}, {"id": 13416, "name": "凉鞋"}, {"id": 13811, "name": "泳装"}, {"id": 18444, "name": "雨衣"}, {"id": 26979, "name": "吹风机"}, {"id": 32857, "name": "Teva"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 40305, "name": "E.I.f"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 100, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170511104203IHE4XR2tyFB9lpnV.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/lvmh-to-launch-fashion-multi-brand-online-store/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 旗下电商 24Sevres.com 即将上线</strong></a> | 该网站将销售 LV、 Dior 、Fendi 等奢侈品在内共 150 个品牌的产品，网站名称的灵感来自集团旗下高端百货 Le Bon Marche 的地址。有消息称，LVMH 的掌舵人 Bernard Arnault 说该网站将于 6 月 6 日正式面向 70 多个国家及地区开放。目前，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.24sevres.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">首页</a>登记电子邮箱，网站会发邮件通知你开放时间。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/e-l-f-beauty-sales-jump-15-percent-in-first-quarter-10885261/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国平价美妆品牌 E.I.f Beauty 第一季度销售大涨 15%</strong></a> | E.I.f 第一季度净销售额为 6060 万美元，上涨了 15%。不过，它的净收入从去年同期的 380 万美元下降到了 220 万美元。该公司的 CEO Tarang Amin 称，E.I.f 在这一季度的出货量有显著的增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Adidas-sells-golf-business-Taylormade-to-buyout-group-KPS,825830.html#.WROuAVK76T8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>adidas 将出售旗下的高尔夫品牌</strong></a> | 周三，adidas 宣布出售旗下的三个高尔夫品牌 Taylor Made、Adams Golf 和 Ashworth Golf，将以 4.25 亿美元的价格，打包卖给新加坡私募基金 KPS Capital。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/nike-iphone-case-air-force-1-roshe\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 推出了 iPhone 7 “鞋底”系列手机壳</a>。该系列手机壳还原了 Air Force 1 和 Roshe 的外底纹路，分别以蓝色、荧光绿和深红色呈现，定价为 35 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095457AC0sTYQdbIy6Vr5t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095457S6IypLaqtYO4nb5e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705110955023ps0AY2nBlyEacP9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/x-girl-uneek-by-keen-2017ss-collaboration\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本品牌 X-GIRL 与 UNEEK by KEEN 推出全新“双绳一垫”联名鞋款</a>，这双鞋的鞋床有稳定足弓之效，还可以自由调整鞋面以贴合脚型。将于 5 月 12 日正式在香港和日本店铺上架，定价 950 港元及 12000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095445pjTt8JZk0DKzR312.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/japan-dyson-supersonic-launch-new-color\" rel=\"nofollow\">戴森的 Dyson Supersonic™ 吹风机发布全新蓝色及配备皮制礼盒的紫色版本</a>，定价分别为 48600 及 59400 日元，暂时只在日本市场售卖。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095414hBMCoNVkw9XQ73Wj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095414isMF1fdYqa3KkHOT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>诞生于 1984 年的美国经典凉鞋品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/teva-2017-ss-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> TEVA 最新一季产品发布。</a>除了经典的 Original Universal 及其升级版之外，还带来了新作 Alp Premier 系列，在经典设计中加入了新的鞋身织带系统，配色的选择也很丰富。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095324uckIftn1H3PheVFZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095325bHcT8I3wNaXhWqtU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095325MDU0wyGtOR2kSZpz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095325txYyKJ2S4TFLN30V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095325m2xB4SU7wGeyc8XQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095325fHN0bYpmUq1XjQGg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051109532679OpildtqrGXSvF3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705110953265O2S7Vg4sYlnfkQu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095326dbnRGNeH8VlUMOp0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095326XZk6NPsoyqgrh2cD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095326l9hgfSatGsIEzeFX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095327PeUsEOo5r798KMJ6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095327gOm5fR4TN9wbSPMy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095327IxmdAoU970Tz1lVY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705110953289eNKFwxpvZ43iWaT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095328AR81NTkYgjqhrC0H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095327CmVN32wEhYDFvTAX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.coneysloft.com/magazine/2017/3/23/marni-x-stutterheim-avant-garde-meets-functional-outerwear\" rel=\"nofollow\">瑞典雨衣品牌 Stutterheim 携手意大利 Marni，带来了几款全新的雨衣设计</a>。这个联名系列融合了 Marni 拿手的撞色风格和 Stutterheim 连帽雨衣原型，将于 7 月上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095229MFPtG8RTVD6iuYeI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095255gWeuTf2ZwL56Fak4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095403qp4sOYHnPEtIWmwK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095403TOKFMvPVAr21Xq0u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>如果你正好在寻找合适的泳装的话，于今年春天刚刚成立的意大利独立泳装品牌 <a href=\"http://www.missmoss.co.za/2017/05/05/lido/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lido</a> 是个不错的选择。Lido 意指威尼斯的一个岛屿，它也是欧洲第一个海滨浴场之一。这个品牌的泳衣全部在威尼斯设计完成，以极简设计为主，搭配了红、深蓝、墨绿等色调，极具复古感。Lido 系列泳装价格多为 100 多欧元左右，<a href=\"http://www.lido-lido.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a>支持邮送全球。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095119N1SCbUP6oaBYM8Jt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095123lLcF9mKO1j2ZdMGN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705110951199CzNSAWG5bf4JYQE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095120JRWCnrAowUjS3kl6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095120Etm0ngaMSdAq5X4T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095120t6vmeR3qQjIigZpO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.815833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095119dMgyBUOVt8ovQqkw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095120dsbq6NDyjFQ3Avzm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095122RbF7uWBsvfjeAtQc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.815833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095122h2JuHqg3rFao59MC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095122DNY9Cf5obiuXRxOp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.815833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095120LofDr6P4ina5RU8e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095121dKE6siyt9RBToOp5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.815833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095121Oa1mtj78F6HiqQk3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095122usJ5kd14VgihHQza.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.265823\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511095122FkepSId028Yx19an.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.225833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.missmoss.co.za/2017/05/05/lido/\" rel=\"nofollow\">missmoss</a></p>"}